{"tid":1810270,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沙田龍華酒店火警傳爆炸聲　消防花半小時撲滅 【註：火警發生地點附近是沙田警署】","createTime":"2020-01-03T17:22:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T17:28:25.000Z","uid":244704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ac92eef088c2607dcd114e6a7f43083c73921227","tid":1810270,"uid":244704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T17:22:57.000Z","msg":"沙田下禾輋村22號龍華酒店，今晚(3日)11時許突然起火，現場熊熊火光，離遠可見，且傳出爆炸聲響，同時有滾滾黑煙席捲半空，有職員發現失火，立即報警求助。消防接報趕至，派出2隊煙帽隊及開動2條喉灌救，約於半小時後將火救熄，火警中無人受傷，毋須疏散。消防正調查起火原因。<br />\n根據資料顯示，龍華酒店是香港最古老的酒店之一，當時為香港僅有的園林酒店，建於戰前的1938年，原為東主鍾秀長的家族的度假別墅，仿照九龍塘的住宅建築，樓高兩層，外形呈四方形，被當地村民稱為「四方樓」。<br />\n隨着沙田新城市發展及沙田新酒店落成．龍華酒店客房逐漸荒廢，又因未能合乎香港的《消防條例》，所以開始關閉酒店業務。1985年開始，龍華酒店開始轉型以純粹餐館方式營運，以紅燒乳鴿為招牌菜，末代港督彭定康亦是熟客，而前中華民國總統蔣經國更派專機來港購買乳鴿，故獲「飛天乳鴿」的美名。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200103/photo/bkn-20200103232604545-0103_00822_001_02b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200103%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200103232604545-0103_00822_001_02b.jpg&h=f44b1a5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200103/photo/bkn-20200103232604545-0103_00822_001_03b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200103%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200103232604545-0103_00822_001_03b.jpg&h=e3300e19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200103/photo/bkn-20200103232604545-0103_00822_001_04b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200103%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200103232604545-0103_00822_001_04b.jpg&h=875163d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200103/photo/bkn-20200103232604545-0103_00822_001_05b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200103%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200103232604545-0103_00822_001_05b.jpg&h=902a7793&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200103/photo/bkn-20200103232604545-0103_00822_001_06b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200103%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200103232604545-0103_00822_001_06b.jpg&h=a9a74b56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200103/photo/bkn-20200103232604545-0103_00822_001_07b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200103%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200103232604545-0103_00822_001_07b.jpg&h=bedc5f15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200103/photo/bkn-20200103232604545-0103_00822_001_08b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200103%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200103232604545-0103_00822_001_08b.jpg&h=616590c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200103/photo/bkn-20200103232604545-0103_00822_001_09b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200103%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200103232604545-0103_00822_001_09b.jpg&h=761e8487&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"054ad7a677a4b9c420d914153a4bf2ed1fea91bc","tid":1810270,"uid":311734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T17:28:25.000Z","msg":"沙田今日又有一單被自殺案，唔知有冇關係"}]}